===Noun===
'''booking'''
# the [[engagement]] of a [[performer]] for a particular [[performance]]
# a [[reservation]] for a [[service]], such as [[accommodation]] in an [[hotel]]
#(''sports'') The issuing of a [[caution]] which is, in theory at least, written down in a book. In practice this may be indicated by showing a [[yellow card]] or [[red card]].

